te><br />\n請問駁唔埋都同係咪 alternative 有咩衝突 ?</blockquote><br />\nMr.A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個野爛架！！！<br />\nLibreWriter打啲字會消失 同LibreWriter 係咪Word 既alternative 有咩衝突？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLibreWriter 打 D 字會消失 同 Opencad D 線駁唔埋唔同<br />\n而且 LibreWriter 打 D 字會消失係咪真係同 LibreWriter 有關都唔知</blockquote><br />\nThis is an analogy, kid.</blockquote><br />\n咁即係你既比喻有問題</blockquote><br />\n自己get唔到就get唔到啦<br />\n<br />\n如果我用word = 做到document <br />\n但librewriter 打啲字會消失，咁仲叫唔叫做到document? <br />\n<br />\n我用autocad = 畫到圖度度到precise呎吋<br />\n如果用個所謂alternative opencad 啲線原來駁唔埋 = 度呎吋有誤差，咁仲叫唔叫度好呎吋？<br />\n<br />\nAlternative 既意思唔係叫同一樣既功能就算得上Alternative，Alternative 既意思係指功能一樣之餘達到我使用原本工具既目的。Mr A 諗清楚先好再死雞撐飯蓋ok?"},{"pid":"5e3bb7b58454c6fee7e2e7eeca45da7d4a8be277","tid":386001,"uid":475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:51:43.000Z","msg":"自己google 搵到就自己用 冇就<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">俾錢買啦撚樣</span>"},{"pid":"a109b3fb675d0b852356bbcfd92f55747a33c1a5","tid":386001,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nMr.A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個野爛架！！！<br />\nLibreWriter打啲字會消失 同LibreWriter 係咪Word 既alternative 有咩衝突？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLibreWriter 打 D 字會消失 同 Opencad D 線駁唔埋唔同<br />\n而且 LibreWriter 打 D 字會消失係咪真係同 LibreWriter 有關都唔知</blockquote><br />\nThis is an analogy, kid.</blockquote><br />\n咁即係你既比喻有問題</blockquote><br />\n另外你幾耐之前用過 Opencad ?</blockquote><br />\n手上持有一份2016q4 IIR<br />\n因為個客香港office 為咗慳錢用linux同openscad，結果因為啲線合唔理度錯晒數，交上廠生產時啲數值唔準，蝕咗2千2百萬<br />\n好彩只係22M姐<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話ms一定最好，因為autocad pc版 都合唔埋啲線（但度數又準架喎），行Mac 版autocad 係接近完美。<br />\n<br />\n有時啲野 唔好未用過就出黎9up，世界會更美好，thanks"},{"pid":"6a349b2053b5ea622b976238fd03d93c271fd302","tid":386001,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nMr.A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個野爛架！！！<br />\nLibreWriter打啲字會消失 同LibreWriter 係咪Word 既alternative 有咩衝突？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLibreWriter 打 D 字會消失 同 Opencad D 線駁唔埋唔同<br />\n而且 LibreWriter 打 D 字會消失係咪真係同 LibreWriter 有關都唔知</blockquote><br />\nThis is an analogy, kid.</blockquote><br />\n咁即係你既比喻有問題</blockquote><br />\n另外你幾耐之前用過 Opencad ?</blockquote><br />\n手上持有一份2016q4 IIR<br />\n因為個客香港office 為咗慳錢用linux同openscad，結果因為啲線合唔理度錯晒數，交上廠生產時啲數值唔準，蝕咗2千2百萬<br />\n好彩只係22M姐<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話ms一定最好，因為autocad pc版 都合唔埋啲線（但度數又準架喎），行Mac 版autocad 係接近完美。<br />\n<br />\n有時啲野 唔好未用過就出黎9up，世界會更美好，thanks</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄會同Mr.A拗，好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9091bf37734d54fa4d1f45ac28395587683b703c","tid":386001,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個野爛架！！！<br />\nLibreWriter打啲字會消失 同LibreWriter 係咪Word 既alternative 有咩衝突？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLibreWriter 打 D 字會消失 同 Opencad D 線駁唔埋唔同<br />\n而且 LibreWriter 打 D 字會消失係咪真係同 LibreWriter 有關都唔知</blockquote><br />\nThis is an analogy, kid.</blockquote><br />\n咁即係你既比喻有問題</blockquote><br />\n另外你幾耐之前用過 Opencad ?</blockquote><br />\n手上持有一份2016q4 IIR<br />\n因為個客香港office 為咗慳錢用linux同openscad，結果因為啲線合唔理度錯晒數，交上廠生產時啲數值唔準，蝕咗2千2百萬<br />\n好彩只係22M姐<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話ms一定最好，因為autocad pc版 都合唔埋啲線（但度數又準架喎），行Mac 版autocad 係接近完美。<br />\n<br />\n有時啲野 唔好未用過就出黎9up，世界會更美好，thanks</blockquote><br />\n條友真係次次都衝出嚟倒鳩Linux米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}